                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7577" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1192</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2344 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">格力电器员工持股计划是激励“员工”的吗？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Is the GREE Electric employee stock ownership plan an incentive for &quot;employees&quot;?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">于培友，李昊，李庆香</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">格力电器股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">格力电器；员工持股计划；激励方案；激励效果</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> GREE Electric, employee stock ownership plan,incentive scheme,effect</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工持股计划作为一种新型的股权激励方式，如今已经成为上市公司完善公司治理结构、提高员工工作积极性和企业凝聚力的重要手段之一。格力电器作为我国空调行业的头部企业，其在混改之前已经连续13年没有实施过任何与股权挂钩的激励措施。格力电器第一大股东变更为珠海明骏后，格力电器顺势发布了第一期员工持股计划，但该计划一经推出就在市场上引发了不小的争议。不少投资者认为该计划存在着严重的利益输送问题，难以对核心员工起到激励作用。本案例描述了格力电器实施员工持股计划的设计方案和实施过程，结合格力电器目前的发展状况，引导学员分析其实施动因及实施效果。帮助学员深入理解员工持股计划的方案设计、作用机理和影响实施效果的关键因素。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a new type of equity incentive, employee stock ownership plan (ESOP) has become one of the important means for listed companies to improve their corporate governance structure and enhance employees&#39; motivation and corporate cohesiveness. GREE Electric, which is the head of Chinese air conditioning industry, has not implemented any equity incentives for 13 consecutive years before the mixed reform. After Hillhouse into the shares, GREE Electric released the first phase of ESOP in a timely manner, but the ESOP sparked considerable controversy in the market once it was launched. Many investors believe that the ESOP has serious benefit transfer problems and can hardly be an incentive for core employees. Our case describes the design and implementation process of GREE Electric&#39;s ESOP, and analyzes the motivation and effectiveness of its implementation in the context of GREE Electric&#39;s current development. This case helps participants gain a deeper understanding of the scheme design, mechanism of action and key factors affecting the effectiveness of the implementation of ESOP.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工持股计划，激励理论，人力资本理论，公司治理理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
